Package main.java.elsim.models

Class Item

java.lang.Object
main.java.elsim.models.Item
public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
An Item is a object that can be transported by a Passenger of an elevator. This Class defines the common attributes like mass and required space that are relevant for the simulation.
